pmPGP 1.3 is a powerful and easy to use OS/2 PM shell for PGP.
pmPGP supports encryption, decryption and digital signatures. 
Shows key signatures in a tree view. Communicates with every application or 
the Workplace via Dra&Drop of files and clipboard. Maintains a history of 
processing. You will need an OS/2 port of PGP to be able to use pmPGP.
Shareware $35.
